desc_short	-----								The Mayor of Anozira wants to breathe some new life into his town and he needs you! Help Al Emmo and the locals bring tourists to Anozira! Explore the town and learn about the local stops and interesting areas as you use your Hidden Object skills to attract new people to the area and help local business survive.							
